item.title: Eben Moglen - 'Freedom in the Cloud' 2/5 @ NYU
item.description: Biella passed this flyer around on the Debian-NYC mailing list. If you are in New York City this Friday, you won’t want to miss this Eben Moglen’s talk. If you can’t see the embedded object, go here or to this post’s permalink.
